# Git Rules
- Work on branch `wow-{% raw %}{{ task.task_id | default("feature") }}{% endraw %}`, never on main
- Commit with trailer: `Co-authored-by: Copilot <223556219+Copilot@users.noreply.github.com>`
- Push branch and create PR: `gh pr create --title "[project] description" --base main`
- No placeholder content — replace every `[INSERT X]` or `TODO` before committing
